      <title>以色列受伤士兵人数不断增加是战争的隐性成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/the-number-of-wounded-israeli-soldiers-is-mounting-representing-a-hidden-cost-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列拉马特甘（美联社）——伊戈尔·图多兰 (Igor Tudoran) 在加沙地带只呆了 12 个小时，一枚导弹就击中了他的坦克，导致他受了致命的伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/the-number-of-wounded-israeli-soldiers-is-mounting-representing-a-hidden-cost-of-war</guid>
